OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain across northern and
OL,6,Fwestern Scotland, though less heavy
OL,7,Fthan Monday. Brief light rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle affects Northern Ireland and
OL,9,Fnorthwest England. Elsewhere, dry with
OL,10,Fplenty of sunshine. Breezy in the
OL,11,Fnorth, with temperatures above average
OL,12,Fand hot further south.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRather cloudy across northern
OL,15,Fareas with occasional rain or drizzle
OL,16,Fin northwest Scotland. Elsewhere, dry
OL,17,Fwith clear spells while patchy fog
OL,18,Fdevelops in the southwest. Warm for
OL,19,Fmany, near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
