OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSaying cloudy with patchy
OL,6,Frain in far northwestern Scotland. Dry
OL,7,Felsewhere with plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FVery warm widely but feeling hot
OL,9,Facross southern and central England in
OL,10,Fthe strong sunshine.
